HEADWORD: Transcriptive
<hw>Tran*scrip"tive</hw> <pr>(-t⟦icr⟧v)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Done as
from a copy; having the style or appearance of a transcription.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> -- <wordforms><wf>Tran*scrip"tive*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> <mark>[R.]</mark></wordforms> <rj><au>Sir T.
Browne.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
